title: Road Tested Ramp Jam ISPO 2014
description:
The Volcom Road-Tested Ramp Jam delivered a serious amount of hammers, bangers and its share of slams too. Check out the highlight video. Congrats to the finalists and thanks for everyone who participated. Electric, Hella Clips, Kingpin Skateboarding, DAMMN, Dogway Skateboard Magazine.

Results:
OSKAR ROSENBERG HALLBERG 1st 2500€
DAAN VAN DER LINDEN 2nd 1200€
FERNANDO BRAMSMARK 3rd 800€
DANNIE CARLSEN 4th 500€
ALEX HALLFORD 5th 400€

- Music - 
Song: Sid
Artist: Dirty Fences
Release: Dirty Fences EP

Full report, video and photos here: http://www.volcomeurope.com/news/arti...
